                     move  "#"            to   w-cnt-pre-exe-pgm
                     go to pre-exe-pgm-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Altrimenti memorizzazione in campo testata      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-dpz-cod-prg        to   w-tes-cod-dpz          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
