      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se default da utilizzare               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tmo-orf        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tmo-orf-def-900.
