      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-def-tmo-orf        to   w-tes-tmo-orf          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tmo-orf-def-900.
       acc-tmo-orf-def-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
