      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Visualizzazione campo chiave : tipo movimento per ordini  *
      *    * fornitori                                                 *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-tmo-orf-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      05                   to   v-car                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      18                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-tmo-orf        to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
       vis-tmo-orf-999.
