      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "BX"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      18                   to   v-lto                  .
           move      80                   to   v-pto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
